          <m>a = 36, b = 60</m>
        </p>
        </statement>
        <answer>
          <p>
            <m>\gcd ( {36, 60} ) = 12</m>, <m>12 = 36 \cdot 2 + 60 \cdot ( { - 1} )</m>
